<node id="OPERATING INCOME">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Operating income is a key financial metric that reflects the profitability of businesses from their core operations before accounting for interest, taxes, depreciation, and amortization. It provides insights into the efficiency and performance of various entities such as Evergreen Consumer Goods Co., Acme Financial Services, HealthPro Innovations, EduCorp, Energen Solutions Ltd., SkyQuest, Innovate Tech Solutions, Green Fields Agriculture Ltd., HealthLife Solutions, Retail Emporium, Entertainment Enterprises Inc., MediaCorp, CleanCo, and others. These companies report their operating income based on the revenue generated from core business activities, which is influenced by market demand, product prices, strategic initiatives, and other factors. For instance, in 2017, SkyQuest reported an operating income of $2.5 billion due to favorable market conditions and price changes, while Innovate Tech Solutions recorded an operating income of $2.4 billion in the same year. Similarly, Entertainment Enterprises Inc.'s operating income reached $500 million due to market demand and product adjustments, contributing significantly to their overall financial performance. Operating income plays a crucial role in assessing the operational efficiency and profitability of businesses, making it an essential component of net profit influenced by cost control measures and business operations.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6d026cea462542fe9fff39ddbfd19828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-979de99b621d84a52967a73e82072fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80c72d37968c0d4dd392d44bd7f5482b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a599832af183fb1ddbe1f6b6731945bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d407571d270f9706da113567619e06d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1238b57cc99d136f545571b9dd82db3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77befee92758f290a343511f6f1115d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d344d0f0729d014025e235637f219b93&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35f37872ab5a23e8c7e73063569a0557&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50483edd8e6c1000eb7e736789f88180&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-714cbaaf56ea79742aa853f7516e9770&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50431f861b4ac4cb22c35dba840f64d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b28065608f1603d4a8a479dda209b62f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ab142ad9445645e3e1229d368cd8cef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215f65f8215fc43b68f8bcda56cf7649&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3ba3b19f710700bf924cad056e368f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c897c0c89be45f0ede6332eaf4d0d702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5925eafb15ed2632cd3580cb051c735a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1aa54f2217f78ca064890ee34b508c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04c9591ce559e53c799750280d94d8d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-697c5b41d7c7bd48216d37965b05628c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cd6c3e411898f8cfce6a7ad09dc1482&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b19a7bd6a19f4a7c30c8940c95a6cc77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc2324ac7343ed62556299e5a404a2cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a446ed05795a0458cd0a88c581d2e68f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4af4e0507f3c6b0cadff3455d5050bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4c9b99e4333c0fc91fadb79678fc9db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b0fe12f1ff41b0d967a78886abaf302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d0212fa7bced9974f545c675c8b2fd9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-653d1e57a155d2cb3e5cc160913b5a4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6936ab982176384c70c7447f82537c1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80f6488e902ec7dd811b35a2e8d844f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d63f21184e3c94e6b269a47169792b4f</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 1}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 42}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 280}]</data>
