<node id="TOTAL ASSETS">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">The data provided outlines various entities' total asset values for different years and contexts. CleanCo's total assets reached $40 million, while HealthPro Innovations valued their total assets at $500 million in 2021. In contrast, Energen Solutions Ltd had a substantial total of $2.3 billion in 2019, influenced by factors like acquisitions, disposals, and revaluations.

Retail Emporium's total assets amounted to $1 billion in 2020, also impacted by similar considerations. InnovateTech's assets totaled $450 million due to various changes including acquisitions, disposals, and revaluations. SkyQuest had significantly higher assets at $5.8 billion, again influenced by such factors.

Other entities like Capital Finance Group and Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc., as well as InnovateTech Solutions, GreenTech Solutions Inc., Culture Innovators Ltd., Vanguard Media Group, Elevate Retail Inc., and Acme Financial Services each had their total asset values determined through similar processes including acquisitions, disposals, revaluations, and overall financial resources.

The company's assets can vary widely depending on various factors such as investments made in 2017, changes over the year, or specific years like 2021 where certain entities reached significant figures. The value of Green Fields Agriculture Ltd.'s total assets was £10,000,000 at the end of 2019.

Overall, these summaries provide a comprehensive view of various companies' asset values across different periods and contexts.</data>
