<node id="SHAREHOLDER EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Shareholder equity is the residual interest in an entity's assets after deducting liabilities, representing ownership value for shareholders. In various entities such as EduCorp, Acme Government Solutions, HealthPro Innovations, Stellar Entertainment Holdings Ltd., Evergreen Consumer Goods Co., Elevate Retail Inc., Entertainment Enterprises Inc., Hudson Consumer Goods Co., and InnovaTech Solutions, shareholder equity reached values ranging from $70 million to $3.5 billion. This total equity belonging to shareholders was influenced by net profit, dividend distributions, capital reserves, and the overall growth and profitability of these companies.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e609b018617055b7d5dc870db1c4757b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f44b736ad3c18f059acfe6fabeb81e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba6eb78874d9f70804ab1afe598d8ead&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-979de99b621d84a52967a73e82072fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e5aafa840eea20d15f2fd8a00fab1ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38d9ec024e38fbc6a7a6898ecfb6a75e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56fd945f7ee2904722489a9bbcdee603&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eae3b2a996621bb1a15dc934c95e4814&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8763228626c21dd52e74133f69994c95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4800ae66a2a5ff51e29e9d98bf5bff61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c112071822c75653b6ec686665652abd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e18719a912a7c4a982ea1e82aabf8c50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2319ae3aae936c5381f060ca9749e8c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77333223cb5bc636246480ec1e5d035&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ecd74e3a93f543a5bd9ecaadcc21203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38010aa7b2a88569eb61b8346ab935a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d81c32016272e93449df5bcbdecd612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24f46a8be819ace615cf5aa0817b5d5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a446ed05795a0458cd0a88c581d2e68f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3ec9f001ef81926442b021a875c1200&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0355673bf5c1875f6a64cd9fc929590c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4af4e0507f3c6b0cadff3455d5050bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57c5a74af7f543384fab8bb3f034a449&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb24595892dedd4181d8b6464212c646</data>
