<node id="DEBT RATIO">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">DEBT RATIO is a financial metric that measures a company's ability to repay its debts, calculated as total liabilities divided by total assets. It provides insights into a company's financial leverage and stability, with lower values generally indicating better financial health. For instance, Energen Solutions Ltd had a debt ratio of 34.78%, while JetWing Aviation and Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc. had ratios of 20% and 0.375 respectively, indicating effective management of debt. CleanCo Housekeeping Services' debt ratio was at 37.5%, EduCorp's at 40%, Entertainment Enterprises Inc.'s at 25%, Evergreen Consumer Goods Co.'s at 59%, GreenTech Solutions Inc.'s at 30%, HealthLife Solutions' at an unspecified rate, HealthPro Innovations' at 40%, Hudson Consumer Goods Co.'s at 0.5, and Innovate Tech Solutions' ratio indicating the proportion of its assets financed by debt. The Debt Ratio also stands as a measure of the company's total liabilities relative to its assets, with lower ratios like 20% or 25% reflecting a more favorable financial position.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-84837225d2fbb62d11b2300e702c1c81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f44b736ad3c18f059acfe6fabeb81e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e5aafa840eea20d15f2fd8a00fab1ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7797019f7dcd61a4d8f88ad2333a2a6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d02b6c8e6e8cd456c8a9353a70ddde0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38d9ec024e38fbc6a7a6898ecfb6a75e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56fd945f7ee2904722489a9bbcdee603&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5779f80597e1eddbd6433584e559f7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d37b4eca9002e95d5b68faa9221f73e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c5c89f876d38d0cafa201755ea563f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810f603e44416b2dcfec53008b130c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5de042ae6be67cff2d5233137efa2b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac5af14f6a39a36be86413e660a52e66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66fc107cbd8ea2b34c7b2cde83feb4fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e18719a912a7c4a982ea1e82aabf8c50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-564848fe2d141e221030c5e57dfa4bca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5925eafb15ed2632cd3580cb051c735a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fd3c6f9dfdf5bdeb6f690cd1cc8c3c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77333223cb5bc636246480ec1e5d035&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e04aa5dcfa6232f360d1ea7cefb89b15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43e239a28184cb84e5cf47fd48c59469&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd80d78db3eb1ea3510a348d6d9efdd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea99b8bc2534faf507b748ef5304e291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2989d5bb79512b0b2b74a6c64c0e9619&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0621bfde96eb5525d6f58e5926c480bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a446ed05795a0458cd0a88c581d2e68f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efd99858d19f5239d4dc3f7c28f04597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24f46a8be819ace615cf5aa0817b5d5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f294cf817b43e8183cc17f3efeae6ae7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c353765838adf7247e5e48544755137</data>
