<node id="ACCOUNTABILITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Accountability is the obligation imposed on an entity or individual for the proper administration of something entrusted to them.&lt;SEP&gt;Accountability refers to the obligation of individuals within an organization to answer for their decisions and actions, promoting integrity and responsibility.&lt;SEP&gt;Another critical aspect improved through the policy revision was accountability among employees and management.&lt;SEP&gt;Another critical component of the organization's framework, ensuring that actions are justifiable and consequences are faced appropriately.&lt;SEP&gt;Another principle of Energex Corporation emphasizing responsibility for actions and decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Improved accountability in decision-making processes following the policy revisions.&lt;SEP&gt;The obligation of the company and its stakeholders to be responsible for their actions and decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;The organization aims to maintain high standards of accountability for all stakeholders involved.&lt;SEP&gt;The policy emphasized accountability, ensuring that all stakeholders are informed about significant company activities and decisions.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-69ec25103b32ec0812bb32097c77f36d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07deb350aa06d1ed7a48e80c0848d625&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f75e8cf0bba26bfc05ac0123c97b6b6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f752c8f54a7b48e80adbc95acbd2668&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cbd6aba0b430906c6a32fc0b627e45e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79775b53e9ac39a96c5b3234f6ae51f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05f30d31a626eb3434fd33087f1ec762&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4efac72d7f34f12b63181e2b212416cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86ea30fd68f0f9f0b47f90673f9b9d67</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 27}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 224}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 561}]</data>
</node>
<node id="STAKEHOLDER ENGAGEMENT">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Artistic Creations Inc. actively engages with its shareholders through the annual meeting, ensuring their input is considered in key decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Increased engagement with stakeholders after implementing new governance practices.&lt;SEP&gt;Involvement of various stakeholders such as employees, shareholders, and the community in decision-making processes.&lt;SEP&gt;MediaCorp's proactive approach in involving various stakeholders, including shareholders, employees, and the public, in its governance processes.&lt;SEP&gt;Stakeholder engagement involves actively involving all parties with an interest in or are affected by the organization's activities, fostering mutual understanding and cooperation.&lt;SEP&gt;Stakeholder engagement involves actively involving and communicating with individuals, groups, or organizations that have a significant interest in or impact on the company's activities and decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Stakeholder engagement was prioritized to foster better communication between Vanguard Media Group and its various stakeholders including shareholders, employees, and the community.&lt;SEP&gt;The corporation actively engages with various stakeholders in the development process.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of involving various parties in the decision-making and operational processes of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The revised policy placed a strong emphasis on engaging with stakeholders to foster trust and better relationships.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-69ec25103b32ec0812bb32097c77f36d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95d3834acf9f0e585a1a373d6da2f626&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07deb350aa06d1ed7a48e80c0848d625&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f513036e332484f983097108f78ccd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f752c8f54a7b48e80adbc95acbd2668&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cbd6aba0b430906c6a32fc0b627e45e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79775b53e9ac39a96c5b3234f6ae51f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05f30d31a626eb3434fd33087f1ec762&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72a33817a1f22a30794b41e13248f1b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86ea30fd68f0f9f0b47f90673f9b9d67</data>
