<node id="ETHICS COMMITTEE">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">An Ethics Committee is responsible for promoting ethical standards and practices within an organization, such as Acme Government Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ethics Committee is an internal body within Culture Innovators Ltd. tasked with reviewing and strengthening ethical standards.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ethics Committee was established by Culture Innovators Ltd. in February 2021 to review and strengthen ethical standards within the organization.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ethics Committee was established to oversee ethical standards and ensure compliance with industry regulations.</data>
