<node id="MARKET DEMAND">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A key driver of the operating income in 2017 was market demand.&lt;SEP&gt;A key factor contributing to the increase in operating income for Entertainment Enterprises Inc. was market demand.&lt;SEP&gt;A key factor influencing Sunrise Holidays' operating income, representing consumer interest and purchasing power within their target market.&lt;SEP&gt;A significant factor driving StrongBuild Construction's operating income was the strong market demand for its products and services.&lt;SEP&gt;Affecting HealthPro Innovations' financial performance and market impact for 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;Capital Finance Group's operating income is significantly influenced by the overall demand for its products and services in the market.&lt;SEP&gt;Influenced CleanCo's financial performance by driving sales and revenue growth.&lt;SEP&gt;Influenced Energen Solutions Ltd's operating income and net profit.&lt;SEP&gt;InnovateTech Solutions' financial performance was significantly driven by strong market demand for its products and services.&lt;SEP&gt;Market demand refers to the level of consumer interest or purchasing power for Green Fields Agriculture Ltd.'s products.&lt;SEP&gt;Refers to the total demand for products or services in a market, influenced by consumer preferences and economic conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;The level of customer demand for housekeeping services, which influences operating income.&lt;SEP&gt;The level of demand for SkyQuest Airlines' services and products.</data>
