<node id="DEBT RESTRUCTURING">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt restructuring is a strategic initiative undertaken by various entities, including Green Fields Agriculture Co., SkyQuest Airlines, JetWing Aviation, Acme Financial Services, Buildcorp Holdings, Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services, Sunrise Holidays, Elevate Retail Inc., Retail Emporium, Energex, Fabrikon Manufacturing Ltd., MediaCorp, HealthLife Solutions, and Vanguard. This process involves renegotiating or reorganizing the terms of existing debts to improve financial stability and repayment ability. The entities involved in debt restructuring have successfully reduced their liabilities by varying amounts ranging from $5 million to $100 million across different years such as 2017, 2018, 2020, and 2021. These actions have positively influenced the financial performance of these companies, improved profitability, enhanced operational efficiency, and optimized capital structures. The process has also helped in reducing total liabilities and managing debt more effectively, thereby improving overall financial health.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11da193716110b798e5ae48dffd4f82d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a9e6bf70d6696c3456b36c575e86433&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba6eb78874d9f70804ab1afe598d8ead&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6c5e71f78a7da5e6ecc070cac11cea0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e5aafa840eea20d15f2fd8a00fab1ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10eae973ae2df1a21ca9d9b241e652bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eec3af8630d19d0fa7ff619f35ef648d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-430bf1a8d8ef2b0bc557d2a4ddd3f0aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-255a72a2c870f8dbe217d29b6c767b31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651abed322e31ea9108123479ffe3b85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0da40766fcbf4e4d363a2c7c04c37293&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29c699027590e30079ff68755ba7eb98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a77e139d00f88b743aebc6ace02096a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9ac34ab93e229e130a6450d29905974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dee298e4680d02ef7876f99623fba25&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77333223cb5bc636246480ec1e5d035&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c626ff3d897b43bf45c2f5b858da2b0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2b648aa6ff4caa10dbf35629a4a6c49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e78a4d8ab1bba9aace178c170b0b4560&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f11a86b5eba4f2538f07fc173ed4dc0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-309c70936668de0a94b6a3a82de78e91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f05c3ed92b3a437ba0696bc706508075&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94500f81d5c2624bf6f67b19869f3d20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be44390396505e0b1daeeea808624c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff88cc392e6531399af3b007d8494d1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27d51f730afff8bd5cdbf7c0658d6b62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8cf9a60dc3531fcfb28107a7bf108d9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db78f7ce7b137b1b39d33070292a5d2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c15aa57fdf3b9b35e23f4f84d049a3d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9169da66ca9130035a59b5a50ea28140&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a7b355483371995660f13f9894ffd081</data>
