  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">An incident involving financial impropriety by a manager at GreenTech Solutions Inc., highlighting concerns over ethical standards within the organization.&lt;SEP&gt;An incident involving fraudulent activities occurred within Acme Financial Services, necessitating a response to maintain ethical standards and integrity.&lt;SEP&gt;An incident involving unethical practices within the National Development Corporation.&lt;SEP&gt;An unauthorized data access incident occurred involving ethics and integrity standards at EcoGuard Solutions in August 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;In February 2020, Acme Financial Services encountered an incident involving fraudulent activities within the organization, impacting its reputation and brand value.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2018, Capital Finance Group faced an ethics and integrity incident when a former employee was found guilty of fraud and corruption.&lt;SEP&gt;The event refers to an ethics and integrity issue involving an employee violating Evergreen Consumer Goods Co.'s code of conduct in August 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;The incident involved an ethics and integrity breach within Sunrise Holidays, specifically related to employee fraud.&lt;SEP&gt;This incident raised concerns about the company's commitment to ethical conduct and transparency, impacting HealthLife Solutions' reputation.</data>
