<node id="GREEN FIELDS AGRICULTURE LTD.">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Green Fields Agriculture Ltd., founded on April 1, 2005 in Sunnydale, California, is an agricultural company specializing in the cultivation and distribution of organic fruits and vegetables. The organization focuses on strategic growth through acquisitions and investments, with a strong emphasis on corporate governance, transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement. With a NASDAQ listing, Green Fields Agriculture Ltd. actively manages its financial aspects including assets, liabilities, shareholder equity, cash flow, debt ratio, and return on equity. In 2021, the company underwent restructuring of its assets and acquired FreshPro in June, enhancing operational stability and protecting stakeholder interests. The organization also prioritizes risk management measures to mitigate potential risks while maintaining a robust internal control system for asset protection, fraud prevention, and accurate financial reporting. Green Fields Agriculture Ltd.'s operations are committed to sustainable development, social responsibility, and environmental protection initiatives, with an ongoing focus on improving its governance structure through enhanced board training, increased independent directors, and optimized decision-making processes.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f4b4822efe27194ee5bde1e9fc1dc4ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44a7664e537c740abf85f646e39bc990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929451646252798bc0091bc633f5c4c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bb6f258c0b62f7d8ecfc11a10485ad7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b3f82a269786461e1f567901a2649b85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d68e6e29d6746293b0cee6d1a86a70a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a7c63b2cf8bb809ad39f414f7bf91f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c35fb35e317cba71d84aecfb107d90a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fda2e1b35685d895e583b5c27e91ce25&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8905729bc7f11661f4189eb98aa6cc77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c99300c6baeee43dd6eee35536ce5415&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25cfc5e2c06677880426efac137badcc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32ebb41015f7e00cf4b8f0f5a5531aa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0a5ad17cd869e2b328b973db9ddcdd86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-921673eab2bce72b5d922634cca48715&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215f65f8215fc43b68f8bcda56cf7649&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5f3d8540e56d94f6eaa7834b3d1d5e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bdeb750a089da2300f69322b3e1d521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c73c7b43034e3f64e816678c034f8bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6ed9b2f2bee6a86e49364ad4324c317&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-217bde5e8de764ba1c508456e0cd0c63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31d893194d02e283591924933c1ce48d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-831744c7d8cf7387a75c19879f52a527&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a44419503e9b25fe586ea79012df521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d0e65c74adb741cea778705965099ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d98e273e2c0db8ecff4e5dc28cf1c693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f6994a63c1ea20eb35e7d62ffd56cec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d807ea5067ccfd67b2b2d73e5884c80c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9169da66ca9130035a59b5a50ea28140&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a419d026d319d60749e2014da7a60e6</data>
