<node id="NATIONAL DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">The National Development Corporation (NDC) is a government-backed organization established on March 1, 1995, specializing in infrastructure development, urban planning, economic growth initiatives, and promoting transparent governance practices. It has been involved in various corporate acquisitions, developments, transportation infrastructure assets management, financial services operations, smart city projects, sustainable energy initiatives, digital infrastructure development, strategic partnerships with private entities for major infrastructure development, and risk management associated with government regulations, economic uncertainties, and market fluctuations.

The NDC is also committed to enhancing operational efficiency through cost control measures, ensuring financial stability, protecting stakeholders' interests, and promoting community engagement. It has reported strong financial performance in 2019 with a net profit of $890 million distributed among shareholders. The organization emphasizes the importance of ethical practices and maintaining stakeholder relationships.

The NDC's strategic emphasis is on renewable energy, equity acquisitions, investments, transparency, and long-term sustainable development. It has streamlined its operations and implemented robust internal controls to manage its activities effectively. Additionally, it has integrated legal updates for compliance and has been actively involved in governance events and policy implementation related transactions.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-21b3e47a29b40c3a404d8c01d9465e5e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6809c28f443077a7e81b4c105a2665a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c667c05c78d19ee13656f55b3c065fe8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-baa5880522486dc96d7456d2807ed2b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f0cbb58bc4d17f2a6aa35d802e2cd76&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ba8283117f0487641d74dba068f4e2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82874a10bb181f24c8cceaeee35de7b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5d7eee4521844ed87d049f73d47d6f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc16871ae8d70624aed6c49e1b152aa0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74ce379e689f26c60f444ebae23f646d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe667e6af245836371e75849d2e2f938&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9dc8826e34469495472669b89c13f619&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9da47f94b3675152f37522004313c73a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e837c8d82c2b3e95fd809470fd6db136&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af886e9a215a2033919e426fae9d639f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99d1ba99d7427e20f7b42b5509c45832&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb366af3541362a381867e50794a770b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-483667af0e29a4cf1d27cb62372cff51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-712a88ee5e5ac8fa473751742d119208&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6b4501ef6c373376167ecb84faca642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32e05de99f2711e026093ebe364a39be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-612ccf0f29953c5d47ab245247ab232d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa8904b12f66cc2d0c59e838b8f86c96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d08b83e323ddd01495bafd75b08333a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b5f7ef60da338993ea62f2f18ea4577&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec3277b52da6f6e909cb23063ebc3a8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73351a89ba26786b558fdc0288e59d2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8f4573a50008017c7cd514a035b93c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e2e5b25d0f3ca64de73d44688655039&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8fd807392a514fb0ae4290279066901&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72a33817a1f22a30794b41e13248f1b2</data>
