<node id="JAMES THOMPSON">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">James Thompson is a former Finance Manager at Yorktown Municipal Office who has been involved in multiple cases of embezzlement, including unauthorized access episodes related to budget accounts and fabricating invoices. He was found guilty of embezzlement involving disaster relief funds and was sentenced to imprisonment in the Quarryville, Yorktown Court. Thompson's fraudulent activities include engaging in fraudulent vendor payments and misappropriating funds from the flood control budget.</data>
