<node id="G. TORRES">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">G. Torres is a defendant involved in multiple legal cases related to the sale of counterfeit registered trademark goods. She has been charged with selling counterfeit goods at her retail store and was convicted for this offense. Additionally, she is also facing charges for being involved in a traffic accident case where injuries were caused. In another incident, G. Torres attempted to conceal evidence by parking her damaged vehicle and arranging repairs to avoid reporting the accident. Furthermore, she knowingly continued to replenish her counterfeit stock through unverified suppliers. The individual resides at 32 Danbury Street, Vandalia and identifies as Hispanic. She works as an owner of a retail store.</data>
