<node id="X. MORGAN">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">The data provided refers to X. Morgan, a female Caucasian born on March 11, 1968, who resides at 85 Yorktown Street, Glenwood. She is the owner of Morgan &amp; Co. Consulting and was involved in legal proceedings at Riverside, Glenwood Court.

X. Morgan has been accused of tax evasion and asset concealment related to her business operations. The descriptions indicate that she transferred sums from business accounts to personal accounts, used a shell company for property acquisition, and inflated expense claims with fake invoices. She faced charges related to tax evasion and asset concealment in relation to her business operations.

X. Morgan was detained by the Riverside Glenwood Procuratorate due to these allegations and had an arrest warrant issued against her. She was arrested on January 25, 2023 following an investigation into tax evasion and asset concealment at Morgan &amp; Co Consulting.

The data also suggests that X. Morgan is facing penalties outlined in Article 203 of Glenwood Court for the tax evasion charges she is currently facing. This indicates a serious legal consequence for her actions as a business professional involved in financial fraud against the state.

Overall, X. Morgan is under investigation and facing multiple legal charges related to tax evasion and asset concealment at Morgan &amp; Co Consulting. She has been formally charged with these crimes and is subject to sentencing where her criminal history will be considered during the proceedings.</data>
