<node id="J. GONZALES">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">J. Gonzalez is a female individual born on August 11th, 1964, residing at 53 Bayside Street in Clarksville. She works as a Senior Inspector in the Clarksville Tax Department and was involved in an incident located at Charleston, Linden Court on December 12th, 2022. J. Gonzalez has been accused of bending the law for personal gain, engaging in repeated corruption activities over time, betraying public trust, and exploiting her official capacity. She is also accused of altering tax records for Sunrise Construction Inc., disclosing confidential information related to ongoing tax investigations, and manipulating tax records to reduce taxes owed by businesses. J. Gonzalez has been sentenced to five years imprisonment for unlawful activities related to her position of trust and was found guilty of abusing power as a Senior Inspector in the Clarksville Tax Department. She is identified as a defendant involved in criminal actions including violent altercations and property damage during December 2022, and exhibited aggressive behavior and assaulted Mr. John Smith at Central Park on December 10th, 2022.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c4c40b186407c48cdc8af9dd47c0bc82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b539eec5bf882455b357eddca4c1a28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb6121d39e3efcd0d69fd869079a8d6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf300bba05920db7f550e838c53c8d0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8ee70ee33ff530141732f1eab398e54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b30b6a46e9f3c7d6283cdc545ef1f148&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbd36c43460be03f301ffb7b47911c2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94360a9657bf599baf920628da688a48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b4f9956c9589f09b179289c891861ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0ffc21bcaab53e70bfb9038ba872c27&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f758f60d792b7b7d50983c82cdc538d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f79109a2740d179c1d3f3437992dfa4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-172d6da3a49c15bcbeb712b5f21d54b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-678677f572d32bba9dbd4372cfce66a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7fbf2ad3a1521ea17bee792fa851f05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2b6495988033e0229816bbb92fd8820&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-271749341a25d544de00aa06e7814c02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a6f7eff212ae42f5482538d613bf09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f1d9af01d5e4f484f30c8091a1f41b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4af1a7e0b8d87eccccb84a68dfd8f182&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0955f1fd1c14554413b2716d03f28b7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4829817fe954a38f9494fef11ec81919&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-076480f5b24d74b7e39a139890231fa8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5090f2847f41b18b5dd2953cf2444b88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85c5617c92ded68a810ab7da57be6e9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c3add5595b15ef807f1c5ba5dbcb2d3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b4d74ade7dfdce29b46f64039ed7afd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af78e318545e0f8c8ed61a7c6b0919f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb7c9bce758622b657c8ec4ad8b8da5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1081c62a1c2812d10f2434979ffdcdc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06405598596d8096e2aa3d9695ee2b24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7092500a55b0369f25aa9fadfaa2292</data>
