<node id="F. JAMES">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">F. James is a female Retail Store Manager born on April 27th, 1960, residing at 39 Knoxville Street, Windsor. She has been involved in several incidents resulting in legal proceedings in Summerville, Windsor Court. The defendant was charged with picking quarrels and provoking trouble in the area, as well as being identified for forcibly damaging a fence and verbally intimidating a resident on March 13th, 2023. F. James is also known to have caused emotional and psychological distress to multiple victims due to her aggressive behavior, including incidents at local parks and retail stores where she engaged in loud arguments with customers, pushed products off shelves, and physically disturbed patrons. On March 10th, 2023, the defendant was involved in an altercation at a retail store leading to physical disturbances among customers. Additionally, on March 18th, 2023, F. James exhibited aggressive behavior in a local park causing widespread panic and subsequent legal consequences. She has also been observed behaving inappropriately at various locations in Summerville. The individual was sentenced for her actions and was arrested following the accumulation of evidence from multiple incidents involving public disturbances, property damage, harassment, and emotional distress caused to victims.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a892148861172f184b1d37b075494244&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a86216e99f906181749f4aba9e4011a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a06ad6ee5e17dfdf3462998384691ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba13444307838e163b6251e840bba4d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e36874cee3c5bd898c163cea03e526cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea532d7ca17d78a409aed8d9de11565e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cf2b96831f1f0df70f9b5c218cea95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da11c5c36590e07056eb78d6dc095a81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18df20ee6df6ae6076b3001a3309fdde&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5edf9b8dd643e840031b293471eaed65&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd3f384ff1c1735e1f40ad668dbed6cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4df5058b69835ee5adad41dfc0735e6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5231f9dd3dccd036e2c0bc1f3a4d91d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09b0578eb6f8eb370b234e947676efc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ad7127bf4b5d21f9a87330f69553ee2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52e4242ef4582caf1bbcf10a12c9b963&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f70a4e20be22d6d0a8ccff038c1ef0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48321e885a9a79bc4931464f42b976d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-045613fb2941f56add853259793e08cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ea588be9d7db8bb3c6df1bc2718dd0f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fde61e09fe84c918422614ece191bc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c71b0a83322463be6b875d2c6526e20b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5da9ce38da191029a70988429ff9f40f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f027355a77122bcb5dc2f67d0446cd8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55621c3ae7464e7ce81386b742903fa7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c8016dd2f1526571b4bde0eec5dee</data>
