</node>
<node id="MASTOIDECTOMY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A surgical procedure performed to remove diseased or infected tissue from the mastoid process of the temporal bone.&lt;SEP&gt;Mastoidectomy is an invasive procedure performed to treat severe infections in the mastoid process of the temporal bone.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5ff2c0697d8cf9d494fd52625b78a313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24cb5713d5db107423471ed1d21a8da8</data>
</node>
