<node id="DELUSIONS">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Delusions are false beliefs that persist despite evidence to the contrary, often a feature of schizophrenia.&lt;SEP&gt;False beliefs that are not based in reality.&lt;SEP&gt;False beliefs that are not based on reality and can be a symptom of certain mental disorders.</data>
