<edge source="EMBEZZLEMENT" target="ARTICLE 384 OF THE PENAL CODE">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">According to Article 384, embezzlement is a criminal offense involving the fraudulent appropriation of public funds entrusted to one's care.&lt;SEP&gt;The crime of embezzlement is explicitly defined in Article 384 of the Penal Code as misappropriating public funds entrusted to one's care.</data>
